                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " AT 62.5 DEGREES. THIS",
                " VALUE WAS CALCULATED USING THE DATA FOR THE REACTION",
                " (1-H-1(N,EL)1-H-1,,DA) AT DIFFERENT ENERGIES, INTER-",
                " POLATED FROM 5 REFERENCES, AND THE MEASURED SHAPE OF",
                " THE INCOMING NEUTRON SPECTRUM."
              ]
            }
